data.description: MOTIVATED SELLER! BRING US AN OFFER! Welcome to this charming home nestled in the heart of Mount Juliet! This timeless residence exudes warmth, character, and modern updates that will captivate any homebuyer. This mid-century modern home is just waiting for your own personal touches. The standout feature of this home is the magnificent sunroom, a true oasis that seamlessly blends indoor and outdoor living. This home is located close to the Cedar Creek Marina where you can rent boats and enjoy a day out on Old Hickory Lake. Being only 40 minutes from Downtown Nashville, it offers a lot of options for entertainment, restaurants and shopping. The current loan is assumable and has a 2.250% interest rate.
